value.raw:
<style>
  :host {
    mixin(--css-column)
    width: 100%;
  }
  custom-selector {
    mixin(--css-column)
    position: fixed;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transform: scale(0);
    background: #fff;
  }
  :host([opened]) custom-selector {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
    transform: scale(1);
    z-index: 100;
  }
</style>
<custom-input>
  <custom-svg-icon icon="arrow-drop-down" slot="after" class="drop"></custom-svg-icon>
</custom-input>
<custom-selector></custom-selector>
